A video of a woman who had to become an instant taxi driver has surfaced on social media. In the post shared on social media she said: “So, today I was a taxi driver from Faraday to MTN bakithi. “Udriver was arguing ne metro bam sprayer nge pepper spray and he couldn’t see. I had to make the pots heels and all.” In the video, the woman can be seen driving the taxi and in the background a voice of a woman can be heard saying people are staring at her. She then jokes and says: "I have a code 14".  